resources.string: Ukonga amandla kuvuliwe, ayikho into enikwe amandla

Nika amadla isiphathi somsebenzi wasemuva ukuze unwebise impilo yebhethri, kodwa izaziso zezinye izinhlelo zokusebnza noma ama-imeyili kungahle kungakwazi ukubuyiswa ngokushesha. Ungaphatha impilo yebhethri ngokungeza noma ususe izinhlelo zokusebenza kusuka kuhlu olumhlophe.
Ukuvula umsebenzi kungaholela ukuthi izinhlelo zokusebenza zingatholi ulwazi lwesikhathi sangempela kusuka ku-inthanethi phakathi kokucisha kwesikrini.
Ukuze lusebenze kahle, lolu hlelo ludinga imvume engeziwe. Sicela uvumele imvume uma ucelwa.
Ukuze lusebenze kahle, lolu hlelo ludinga izimvume ezingeziwe. Sicela uphathe izimvume ze-%s kumasethingi.

Ukuvula umsebenzi kungaholela ukuthi izinhlelo zokusebenza ezine-alamu noma imisebenzi yezaziso zingakwazi ukuvusa idivayisi ngesikhathi. Kuyancomeka ukuthi ungeze lezo zinhlelo zokusebenza ekuvukeni kwesikhathi kusuka ekhasini lamasethingi.
